N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 48.3 - Conformance with local and other regulations

State Regulations

The Authority expects all on-premises licensees, regardless of type of premises, to conform with all applicable building codes, fire, health, safety and governmental regulations. Notes
